main event: Two cigar-shaped, bright orange objects were seen flying wing-to-wing, then one object seemed to drop below the other. They had pointed tails with contrails, and were traveling from north to south.
interesting points: The objects were moving up and down.
The objects faded out in the distance.
The report states that the objects were likely unidentified aircraft rather than a UFO.
The report was filed by a civilian witness.
